column108: Haven Restaurant og Bar, Kragerø, Norway, is looking for a chef. Job description Production and preparation in the kitchen. Preparation of menu dishes – a la carte Participate in company and catering assignments. Must be able to work independently in and outside Haven Restaurant. Contribute to menu planning and good kitchen finances. Tackle a busy day with a good mood. Skills Good experience with a la carte. Be able to work fast with good quality Speak and understand English Working hours Shift between 10 am and 11 pm Period 15. May 2025 end 31 August 20251 June 2025 end 31 August 2025.  Salary NOK 230 per hour We help with accommodation. More information Ragnar Brevik, +47 9166 2200 How to apply? Send CV to post@haven-restaurant.no Latest application date is 15. May 2025 (from NAV EURES Norway) Haven Restaurant is an unformal dining and meeting place. We focus on simple, tasty dishes based on fresh products. Our desire is to give our guests a pleasant overall experience in a relaxed environment. Good taste sensations with panoramic views to Kragerø harbor basins. 170 seats outside and 80 inside. www.haven-restaurant.no
